wiki.content: Despite having a classic nostalgic theme in the lyrics about "the good old days" this is one of The Strokes most upbeat and positive songs. The music video for the song features The Strokes at a bar having fun, as well as a game of the American game show "Family Feud" played between the Strokes and the legendary indie rock act Guided by Voices. "See, alone we stand, together we fall apart. Yeah, I think I'll be alright. I'm working so I won't have to try so hard. Tables, they turn sometimes. Oh, someday..." Written by Julian Casablancas Performed by The Strokes User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
